item.description:
Actual demo may not start until closer to 5:30-6PM. Heavy traffic from NY.


Starting at 4:00PM we will have all 5 "Tiderace Sea Kayak" boats for demo and/or purchase for anyone that is interested. This will continue until it gets dark. The event will take place in conjunction with the Ocean Skills Session that begins at 6PM. Demos will be restricted to the launch area and will not be on the ocean side.


Low Tide Aug. 18th is 4:09 p.m.

Put-in is at Seabrook Harbor, on the Seabrook side of the bridge on Rte 1A in the large parking lot with a restroom.

Feel free to contact Doug Mogill with any questions on the demo.
item.name: "Tiderace Kayak" Demo Day at Seabrook Harbor Ocean Skills / Surf Session
